# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# x402 Client — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# REQUIRED: Your EVM private key (testnet wallet only — NEVER use a mainnet key)
#
# How to get a testnet wallet + USDC:
#   1. Generate a new keypair:
#      npx cast w new   (requires Foundry: https://getfoundry.sh)
#      OR use any wallet (MetaMask, etc.) and export the private key.
#
#   2. Fund with testnet USDC on Base Sepolia:
#      Visit: https://portal.cdp.coinbase.com/products/faucet
#      Network: Base Sepolia
#      Token: USDC
#
#   3. Copy the private key (with 0x prefix) below:
#

EVM_PRIVATE_KEY=0xYOUR_PRIVATE_KEY_HERE

# Optional: override the server URL (defaults to http://localhost:4021)
# X402_SERVER_URL=http://localhost:4021
